00:15:21.879 --> 00:15:23.440
I came back specifically to see you.

00:15:24.240 --> 00:15:26.360
But I really have important things to do later.

00:15:26.679 --> 00:15:28.399
You want to arrange my funeral?

00:15:31.039 --> 00:15:32.279
Fine.

00:15:33.480 --> 00:15:35.720
Mom has only one request.

00:15:36.200 --> 00:15:37.720
In the future, don't put me

00:15:37.720 --> 00:15:40.840
together with your shabby old father.

00:15:43.720 --> 00:15:45.120
We'll just fight and bicker.

00:15:46.039 --> 00:15:47.279
What are you saying?

00:15:49.799 --> 00:15:50.639
Alright, alright.

00:15:51.919 --> 00:15:53.200
Then I'll leave when you're better.

00:15:53.320 --> 00:15:54.080
You're not leaving?

00:15:54.960 --> 00:15:55.879
Okay.

00:15:56.120 --> 00:15:57.840
If I say I won't leave, I won't.

00:15:58.759 --> 00:15:59.440
Zhen'er

00:15:59.840 --> 00:16:01.200
That Fan family household

00:16:01.960 --> 00:16:04.159
is lonely and hopeless.

00:16:16.480 --> 00:16:17.879
I'll still find you a doctor.

00:16:17.960 --> 00:16:20.639
Doctor Zhao won't work.

00:16:21.120 --> 00:16:22.159
He won't do it.

00:16:31.440 --> 00:16:33.360
It's all my fault for having bad ideas.

00:16:33.919 --> 00:16:34.720
For peace of mind,

00:16:35.000 --> 00:16:36.279
I insisted on coming here for a look.

00:16:37.519 --> 00:16:38.720
It's just that for the moment,

00:16:39.480 --> 00:16:40.440
I probably can't leave.

00:16:42.039 --> 00:16:42.679
How about

00:16:42.919 --> 00:16:44.159
I go find the Eldest Young Master?

00:16:44.720 --> 00:16:46.159
It's more convenient for me alone.

00:16:47.519 --> 00:16:48.440
Maybe right now,

00:16:48.919 --> 00:16:50.320
that really is the only way.

00:16:51.559 --> 00:16:52.639
But you must be careful.

00:16:52.919 --> 00:16:53.960
Don't let anything happen.

00:16:54.360 --> 00:16:55.759
Otherwise I have no way

00:16:55.759 --> 00:16:57.080
to explain to the Old Master and Sha'er.

00:16:57.679 --> 00:16:58.679
Don't worry, Young Mistress.

00:17:01.240 --> 00:17:02.679
You must help me find Sha'er.

00:17:03.759 --> 00:17:04.360
I'm going then.

00:17:21.839 --> 00:17:25.119
Chilis burn the mouth, peppers numb the lips.

00:17:25.799 --> 00:17:26.720
Medicinal herbs

00:17:27.400 --> 00:17:28.599
are burnt and bitter.

00:17:29.519 --> 00:17:30.559
Boiled in one pot,

00:17:31.079 --> 00:17:32.839
why do so many people like to eat it?

00:17:34.160 --> 00:17:35.039
Mainly, it's about

00:17:35.200 --> 00:17:37.559
the blend and the ratio.

00:17:38.079 --> 00:17:39.119
It must be

00:17:39.960 --> 00:17:41.640
a He marrying a Jiang.

00:17:42.240 --> 00:17:43.440
A perfect match.

00:17:45.000 --> 00:17:46.279
Come, come, you try.

00:17:47.519 --> 00:17:48.200
Come on.

00:17:51.519 --> 00:17:53.000
Why are you teaching me this?

00:17:53.400 --> 00:17:54.880
You being the chef is enough.

00:17:57.519 --> 00:17:59.400
I can't stay here forever.

00:18:00.200 --> 00:18:01.720
I'll have to leave sooner or later.

00:18:05.759 --> 00:18:06.759
You've been out so long,

00:18:07.480 --> 00:18:08.799
doesn't your Missus miss you?

00:18:08.960 --> 00:18:10.279
Of course she misses me.

00:18:10.400 --> 00:18:11.519
If she misses you, why not come find you?

00:18:11.960 --> 00:18:14.039
If it were me, I'd have run over long ago.

00:18:14.880 --> 00:18:15.960
She's different from you.

00:18:17.559 --> 00:18:19.039
I actually don't want her to come find me.

00:18:19.319 --> 00:18:21.279
The world is so chaotic right now.

00:18:22.000 --> 00:18:22.720
She should just stay at home.

00:18:22.720 --> 00:18:24.920
Waiting obediently for me to return is enough.

00:18:25.440 --> 00:18:27.880
If you leave, I can go with you.

00:18:29.119 --> 00:18:30.000
How can you leave?

00:18:30.480 --> 00:18:31.599
If you leave, what about your dad?

00:18:32.079 --> 00:18:32.799
Besides,

00:18:33.039 --> 00:18:35.400
your dad wouldn't let you go either.

00:18:36.599 --> 00:18:37.680
This business

00:18:38.480 --> 00:18:40.440
is saved for the two of you.

00:18:40.920 --> 00:18:42.960
You must master the secret recipe.

00:18:43.720 --> 00:18:44.480
If you don't master it,

00:18:46.000 --> 00:18:46.759
what will you do?

00:18:47.559 --> 00:18:48.680
I haven't finished teaching.

00:18:49.440 --> 00:18:51.079
Tired of learning today, learn another day.

00:18:56.839 --> 00:18:57.400
Master.

00:18:58.400 --> 00:18:59.279
Why did you come in?

00:18:59.680 --> 00:19:00.880
Without my permission,

00:19:01.279 --> 00:19:02.960
