00:19:03.279 --> 00:19:04.000
Get out.

00:19:21.400 --> 00:19:22.759
This is money I earned myself

00:19:23.000 --> 00:19:23.880
You don't need to worry about me

00:19:24.359 --> 00:19:25.160
You just count yours

00:19:25.880 --> 00:19:26.880
I came to catch my breath

00:19:28.400 --> 00:19:29.880
You ran underground just to catch your breath?

00:19:33.880 --> 00:19:35.039
Aren't you a fortune teller?

00:19:35.839 --> 00:19:36.559
Read my fortune

00:19:36.880 --> 00:19:37.559
Five copper coins

00:19:39.720 --> 00:19:40.640
Put it on my tab

00:19:40.920 --> 00:19:41.640
That works too

00:19:44.559 --> 00:19:45.079
What are we reading?

00:19:46.200 --> 00:19:47.000
Me and Brother Fan

00:19:48.079 --> 00:19:48.519
Our affinity

00:20:04.839 --> 00:20:07.000
Will it work out or not?

00:20:07.400 --> 00:20:08.920
It might work

00:20:08.920 --> 00:20:10.640
And it might not

00:20:11.079 --> 00:20:12.559
The signs are a bit complex

00:20:12.920 --> 00:20:14.759
I don't know how to explain it to you

00:20:15.000 --> 00:20:15.720
I know

00:20:17.240 --> 00:20:18.079
If it works

00:20:18.960 --> 00:20:20.200
I can't replace Sister Yuzhen

00:20:20.200 --> 00:20:21.279
To be his only one

00:20:22.359 --> 00:20:23.359
If it doesn't work

00:20:24.880 --> 00:20:26.039
I can't let go myself

00:20:36.519 --> 00:20:38.240
You figured it out better than I did

00:20:39.599 --> 00:20:42.079
Ask what love is in this world

00:20:43.279 --> 00:20:45.759
You're still the most reliable one

00:20:47.640 --> 00:20:52.319
Everything in the world has its conqueror

00:20:52.839 --> 00:20:53.880
You surnamed Huo

00:20:54.480 --> 00:20:58.160
You strike first, I'll strike back

00:21:01.640 --> 00:21:02.279
Brother Fan

00:21:03.039 --> 00:21:04.000
I just want to ask you one thing

00:21:04.440 --> 00:21:05.960
Do you have any feelings for me at all?

00:21:09.519 --> 00:21:10.240
Don't say it

00:21:10.680 --> 00:21:11.839
I don't care if you do or not

00:21:12.160 --> 00:21:13.039
I have feelings for you

00:21:13.720 --> 00:21:14.720
I saved your life

00:21:14.960 --> 00:21:15.799
And took you in

00:21:16.319 --> 00:21:18.079
Don't think just because you saved me from the Huos

00:21:18.079 --> 00:21:18.960
That we're even

00:21:19.160 --> 00:21:20.039
We can't be even

00:21:23.799 --> 00:21:24.440
I also...

00:21:24.440 --> 00:21:26.519
...never wanted to be even with you

00:21:31.440 --> 00:21:32.200
Really?

00:21:34.440 --> 00:21:35.279
But Xiugu

00:21:37.599 --> 00:21:40.000
You know I have a Missus

00:21:40.000 --> 00:21:41.160
I don't care

00:21:42.839 --> 00:21:45.640
I can't even manage myself right now

00:21:46.599 --> 00:21:48.039
How can I take good care of you?

00:21:48.039 --> 00:21:49.640
I can take care of myself

00:21:52.920 --> 00:21:56.119
I'm a person with a lot of troubles

00:21:56.920 --> 00:21:58.680
If you knew my past

00:21:59.480 --> 00:22:01.799
You wouldn't have dared to take me in back then

00:22:01.799 --> 00:22:03.200
How do you know what I would've done?

00:22:04.680 --> 00:22:06.240
Then tell me everything

00:22:06.839 --> 00:22:07.720
I'll decide for myself

00:22:10.000 --> 00:22:10.599
Alright

00:22:18.039 --> 00:22:20.279
Uncles, Aunties.

00:22:20.559 --> 00:22:23.000
Let me say a word for Xiugu.

00:22:23.000 --> 00:22:25.240
About my big event from before.

00:22:30.319 --> 00:22:31.279
It's like this.

00:22:32.640 --> 00:22:34.519
Every time he teaches Xiugu,

00:22:34.880 --> 00:22:36.240
he's always very careful.

00:22:36.920 --> 00:22:38.279
I haven't had a chance to make a move yet.

00:22:38.759 --> 00:22:40.079
Just give me a little more time.

00:22:40.319 --> 00:22:41.559
No matter what method you use,

00:22:41.920 --> 00:22:42.880
the sooner the better.

00:22:43.519 --> 00:22:43.920
Okay.

00:22:44.160 --> 00:22:46.359
Once you get the hotpot base recipe,

00:22:46.759 --> 00:22:48.160
your mother's herbal medicine

00:22:48.640 --> 00:22:49.640
won't be a worry anymore.

00:22:50.599 --> 00:22:52.559
Thank you, Young Master Huo. Thank you, Young Master Huo.

00:22:55.720 --> 00:22:56.680
Hurry up.

00:22:57.240 --> 00:22:57.920
Okay, okay.

00:23:03.200 --> 00:23:04.400
I expected it.

00:23:04.400 --> 00:23:05.799
I just didn't expect it to be this fast.

00:23:07.640 --> 00:23:08.640
Boss Fan.

00:23:08.920 --> 00:23:11.119
No wonder your business keeps getting bigger.

00:23:11.200 --> 00:23:13.400
The way you cooperate is quite innovative too.

00:23:13.759 --> 00:23:15.279
And you're willing to yield profits.

00:23:16.559 --> 00:23:18.000
You flatter me, Commander Qin.

00:23:18.400 --> 00:23:20.920
You are the best official under heaven.

00:23:21.200 --> 00:23:22.680
With Commander Qin joining us,

00:23:23.079 --> 00:23:25.920
I think our business will go even more smoothly.

00:23:26.400 --> 00:23:27.160
Commander Qin.

00:23:27.279 --> 00:23:29.480
I'm late, I'm late.

00:23:30.799 --> 00:23:32.680
Boss Fan, there's something you don't know.

00:23:32.920 --> 00:23:35.240
Young Master Huo is the top dog in our town.

00:23:35.359 --> 00:23:37.880
Often, his information is faster than mine.

00:23:39.279 --> 00:23:40.039
Then...

00:23:40.400 --> 00:23:43.000
Commander Qin, you have to be careful.

00:23:43.720 --> 00:23:45.599
Your movements, your assets...

00:23:46.000 --> 00:23:47.599
aren't they all in

00:23:47.799 --> 00:23:49.400
Young Master Huo's hands?

00:23:50.279 --> 00:23:51.640
You two must be joking.

00:23:51.880 --> 00:23:54.160
I'm just the bridge connecting you two.

00:23:54.440 --> 00:23:56.240
Of course I have to care about you both constantly.

00:23:57.599 --> 00:23:59.160
The Huo family in this town...

00:23:59.359 --> 00:24:01.279
has been one of the best for generations.

00:24:01.519 --> 00:24:02.680
I believe Young Master Huo

00:24:02.680 --> 00:24:04.880
has also inherited the family's grand vision.

00:24:05.559 --> 00:24:06.480
How about this time,

00:24:06.960 --> 00:24:08.880
let me and Boss Fan handle this small business

00:24:08.880 --> 00:24:10.000
just for fun.

00:24:10.200 --> 00:24:12.240
Commander Qin, there must be some misunderstanding.

00:24:12.240 --> 00:24:14.279
We signed a contract, didn't we?

00:24:15.920 --> 00:24:16.519
Look, look.

00:24:17.160 --> 00:24:20.200
A three-party contract, signed and sealed.

00:24:24.559 --> 00:24:25.839
Well, Young Master Huo.

00:24:26.160 --> 00:24:28.599
Commander Qin and I discussed it.

00:24:28.880 --> 00:24:30.079
This hotpot business...

00:24:30.599 --> 00:24:31.680
the profit is too small.

00:24:32.319 --> 00:24:33.680
It's not worth Young Master Huo's attention.

00:24:34.440 --> 00:24:35.119
Young Master Huo,

00:24:35.400 --> 00:24:37.400
thanks for letting us have it.

00:24:37.680 --> 00:24:40.079
Next time there's a big deal, we'll work together again.

00:24:44.160 --> 00:24:44.839
Fine.

00:24:45.359 --> 00:24:45.920
Fine.

00:24:46.480 --> 00:24:48.200
Since Commander Qin has decided so,

00:24:48.400 --> 00:24:50.039
Commander Qin must have his reasons.

00:24:50.480 --> 00:24:52.079
I also sincerely wish Commander Qin

00:24:52.279 --> 00:24:54.079
and Boss Fan

00:24:55.240 --> 00:24:58.000
a booming business and rolling in money.

00:24:58.400 --> 00:25:00.119
Good, then it's settled.

00:25:00.240 --> 00:25:01.079
Come, come.

00:25:01.599 --> 00:25:02.920
Attention!

00:25:03.319 --> 00:25:03.839
Look.

00:25:04.160 --> 00:25:05.759
I have plenty of men and trucks here.

00:25:06.000 --> 00:25:07.400
We'll do as you said.

00:25:07.480 --> 00:25:09.839
Like I said, I have high hopes for you.

00:25:12.279 --> 00:25:13.039
Attention!

00:25:13.720 --> 00:25:14.440
At ease!

00:25:15.640 --> 00:25:17.000
Attention! At ease!

00:25:18.359 --> 00:25:19.400
Little officers,

00:25:19.400 --> 00:25:21.359
you all have to listen to my arrangements from now on.

00:25:22.319 --> 00:25:24.359
You are to follow Boss Fan's orders from now on.

00:25:24.440 --> 00:25:25.000
Do you hear me?

00:25:25.200 --> 00:25:26.079
Yes, sir!

00:25:36.160 --> 00:25:37.680
Folks and neighbors

00:25:37.920 --> 00:25:40.279
Dongshihui Hotpot Flagship Store

00:25:40.519 --> 00:25:43.039
is officially open today

00:25:46.720 --> 00:25:48.559
Eat 'em poor! Eat 'em poor!

00:25:48.559 --> 00:25:50.440
Eat the boss poor!

